Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.87,0:33:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,the apps of everyone in this
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.03,0:33:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,room.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.52,0:33:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Your feedback really helps us
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.78,0:33:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,prioritize our work.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.59,0:33:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,For more information about
